title: Swedish royals expecting first child
text:
> Top News Swedish royals expecting first child FILE - A Saturday, June 13, 2015 file photo showing Sweden's Prince Carl Philip sitting with his bride, Sofia Hellqvist in a carriage, after their wedding ceremony, in Stockholm, Sweden. The Swedish royal court said Thursday Oct. 15, 2015 that Prince Carl Philip and his bride Princess Sofia are expecting their first child in April next year. (Mikael Fritzon/TT via AP, File) SWEDEN OUT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
